&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chief Cardiac Physiologist- Echocardiography - Band 8a&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a highly experienced Chief Cardiac Physiologist at Chelsea and Westminster NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post Holder will be managing the Echocardiography department at West Middlesex Hospital and work closely with the Echocardiography lead at Chelsea and Westminster site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful appointee will be responsible for the clinical development of the team and for the optimization of the department resources in order to provide an efficient and robust service to both inpatients and outpatients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameLara LopesJob titleHead of DiagnosticsEmail addresslara.lopes@chelwest.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
